quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"SĀD (S). [Bachi gaŋ ŋɔ maa wuhirimi ni Alkur’aani nyɛla Muɣujizah (lahiʒibsi din ka ŋmali), dama so ʒi di fasara naɣila Naawuni]. M (Mani Naawuni) po Alkur’aani shεli din mali teebu"
  38,2,Chɛli gba! Ninvuɣu shεba ban niŋ chεfuritali maa kuli bela maŋ’ tibgibu mini namgbankpeeni (ni Annabi Muhammadu)
  38,3,"Di zooiya ka Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) niŋ tiŋgbani shɛli hallaka pɔi ni bana (Makka chɛfurinima), ka bɛ kuhi (bɔri sɔŋsim), ka di lahi pala saha shεli bɛ ni yɛn tooi zo n-tilgi"
  38,4,"Kɛ bɛ (Larbunim’) niŋ lahiʒiba domin wa’azulana so (Annabi Muhammadu) kaba na bɛ puuni zuɣu. ka chεfurinim’ maa naan yεli: “Ŋumbɔŋɔ nyɛla sihiralana, ni ʒirilana titali.”"
  38,5,"(Ka bɛ lahi yεli): “Di ni bɔŋɔ, o (Muhammadu maa) zaŋla duumanim’ zaasa leei duuma yino? Achiika! Ŋɔ maa shiri nyɛla lahiʒibsi bini.”"
  38,6,"Ka bɛ puuni asanzanim’ chaŋ (n-ti yεli: “Cham ya n-ti niŋ suɣulo ni yi buɣa jɛma, achiika! Ŋɔ maa nyɛla yɛltɔɣa shɛli ka bɛ bɔra (ni bɛ zaŋ li m- birgiya)"
  38,7,"Tinim’ na ʒin wum ŋɔ maa tatabo adiini shεli din kana bahigu ŋɔ puuni (Annabi Issa daadiini), ŋɔ maa pala shεli m-pahila ʒiri ka o (Muhammadu) ŋma.”"
  38,8,"“Di ni bɔŋɔ, o (Muhammadu) koŋko sani ka bɛ (Naawuni) siɣisi teebu (Alkur’aani) na ti puuni? Chɛli gba! Bɛ (chεfurnim’) bela zilsigu puuni ni teebu (Alkur’aani). Chɛli gba! Bɛ na bi lamla azaaba"
  38,9,"Bee bɛ sani ka a Duuma so Ŋun nyɛ Nyεŋda, ni Pintira nambɔzɔhigu arzichi sɔŋbu shee be"
  38,10,"Bee bɛ malila sagbana ni tiŋgbani, n-ti pahi din be di sunsuuni yiko? Tɔ! (Di yi nyɛla lala), bɛ dum zuɣusaa (n-ti mɔŋ Alkur’aani aayanim’ sheebu na Annabi Muhammadu sani)"
  38,11,"Bɛ (chɛfurinim’) nyɛla tobbihi shɛba bɛ ti yɛn ti tuhi nyɛŋ ba nimaa ni (Badar tobu ni), ka bɛ be laɣinsi puuni"
  38,12,"Annabi Nuhu niriba daa labsi o ʒirilana pɔi ni bana (Makka chɛfurinima), ni Aadunima (Annabi Hudu niriba), n-ti pahi Fir’auna so ŋun daa nyɛ bandilana (ankufunimlana) la"
  38,13,"Ni Samudunima (Annabi Sālihu niriba), ni Annabi Lutu niriba, n-ti pahi Annabi Sayibu niriba, bannim’ maa daa nyɛla laɣinsi"
  38,14,"Bɛ zaɣiyino kam daa bi niŋ shɛli m- pahila bɛ labsila bɛ tuumba ʒirinima, ka azaaba niŋ talahi bɛ zuɣu"
  38,15,"Yaha! Bɛ (Makka chεfurinim’ maa) bi guhiri shεli m-pahila tahigu yim zuɣu (ka Dunia yiɣisi), di mi ti ka ŋmaabu"
  38,16,"Ka bɛ (chεfurinim’ maa) naan yεli: “Yaa ti Duuma (Naawuni)! Tim ti ti tarli (azaaba) yomyom’ pɔi ni saliya karibu dabsili maa"